'''法蘭索瓦·歐容'''（{{lang-fr|'''François Ozon'''}}，{{bd|1967年|11月15日}}）是一名法國導演及編劇，作品常以尖銳嘲諷的幽默與不受拘束的觀點處理性題材，被認為是法國電影「新新浪潮」的代表導演之一。<ref name=jq>Palmer, Tim "Style and Sensation in the Contemporary French Cinema of the Body", ''Journal of Film and Video'', Fall 2006 {{cite web |url=http://www.uncwil.edu/filmstudies/faculty/documents/PalmerJFVarticle.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2010-05-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100602235125/http://www.uncwil.edu/filmstudies/faculty/documents/PalmerJFVarticle.pdf |archivedate=2010-06-02 }} Access date: 14 May 2010.</ref>

